This folder contains scripts that add new commands to GDB. These new commands 
enhanced support for debugging HPX applications.

To add these commands to GDB append the following lines to '.gdbinit' file in 
your home directory.

directory [ABSOLUTE PATH WHERE THE SCRIPTS ARE PRESENT]
source hpx_prefix_cmd.py
source print_var.py
source cmd_parcel.py
source hpx_frame_filter.py

Commands List:
hpx print
info parcels

Use the 'help' command to learn about the usage for these commands.
